Attribution

Hero combat stats (stats.abilities.*, stats.health, stats.armor, stats.shields,
sub_role) are sourced from the Overwatch Fandom Wiki
(https://overwatch.fandom.com/) and are made available here under CC-BY-SA 3.0,
matching the license of the upstream source.

Perks, ability descriptions, roles, and portraits are sourced from Blizzard
Entertainment's official hero pages (https://overwatch.blizzard.com/en-us/heroes/).
Those fields are reproduced here under a claim of fair use / nominative use for
the purpose of enabling Claude.ai-hosted conversations to reference current
Overwatch hero data; they remain the intellectual property of Blizzard
Entertainment.

Per-hero source URLs are enumerated in `ATTRIBUTION.md` in this directory and
in the `metadata.sources` block of every JSON file.

See the root `LICENSE` file for the license covering the scraper source code
(MIT).
